Hey alfredo, I know this is a super late response to your question, but I just stumbled across the same issue and believe I figured out why it happens at least. The problem is that the Inroduction to Alexa series was initially published with the older Alexa SDK and now the first two courses have been update to the newer version, while the later two have not been. The course requests that we use a serverless app repository blueprint that no longer seems to exist in the repo. So, long story short, we either have to wait for the course to be updated or read up on the GitHub documentation (linked here ).

